==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chlorination
<hw>Chlo`ri*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
process of subjecting anything to the action of chlorine; especially, a
process for the extraction of gold by exposure of the auriferous
material to chlorine gas.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chlorine</ent>⟦br⟧
